      "author_association" : "MEMBER",
      "body" : "I use the hex notation here because it's much more obvious. People might not recognize 32767 as the largest 16-bit signed integer, or 16777215 as the largest 24-bit signed integer; but in the hex notation this is immediately clear.\r\n\r\nIt's just more readable to reviewers.",
